narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: the class project is very interesting.

Very cool stuff, but expect nothing in the way of foundations. Just neat techniques, pretty modern stuff... cool applications of some probability and graph-theory concepts you've probably seen before. Go for it
Yes definitely. The material is very pretty, and the professor is great.
* I would absolutely recommend this course to another student.
